<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Confirmation | Hedgeon Finance Capital</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d8b67, #0a6e4f);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: #ffd43b;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #444;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .message {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #f0f9f6;
            border-left: 4px solid #0d8b67;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .security-tips {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .security-tips h3 {
            color: #0d8b67;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .security-tips ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .security-tips li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #0d8b67, #0a6e4f);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(13, 139, 103, 0.25);
        }

        .action-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(13, 139, 103, 0.35);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin: 15px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #0d8b67;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .copyright {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #888;
        }

        .icon {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .greeting {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Hedgeon<span>Finance</span></div>
            <h1>Password Reset Confirmation</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Hello <strong>
                    <%= userName %>
                </strong>,</div>

            <div class="message">
                <p>Your Hedgeon Finance Capital account password has been successfully reset.</p>

                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <p>If you initiated this password reset, no further action is required. Your account security has
                        been updated.</p>
                </div>

                <p>This confirmation is sent to verify that your password has been changed. If you did not request this
                    change, please contact our security team immediately.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="https://www.hedgeonfinance.com/auth/login" class="action-button">Access Your Account</a>
            </div>

            <div class="security-tips">
                <h3>
                    <span class="icon">ðŸ”’</span>
                    Security Recommendations
                </h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use a unique password that you don't use on other websites</li>
                    <li>Enable two-factor authentication for added security</li>
                    <li>Update your password regularly (every 60-90 days)</li>
                    <li>Never share your login credentials with anyone</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>Hedgeon Finance Capital</p>
                <p>250 Financial District, New York, NY 10005</p>
                <p>support@hedgeonfinance.com | (800) 555-0123</p>
            </div>


            <div class="copyright">
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Hedgeon Finance Capital. All rights reserved.<br>
                    This email was sent to you as a registered user of Hedgeon Finance Capital.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>